器" data-id="107278" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-bottom: -12px;margin-left: 6px;outline: 0px;width: 27px;visibility: visible;"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 334.6 286.9" style="visibility: visible;"><polygon style="fill: rgb(245, 202, 70);visibility: visible;" points="334.6,286.9 185.3,286.9 185.3,0.4 334.6,150.4 "></polygon><polygon style="fill: none;stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width: 6;stroke-miterlimit: 10;visibility: visible;" points="147.6,283.9 3.3,283.9 3.3,7.4 147.6,150.4 "></polygon></svg></section><section style="padding-top: 20px;padding-right: 25px;padding-left: 11px;outline: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 253, 244);visibility: visible;text-align: left;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;"></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">解放军核潜艇，刚</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">有动静，日本就按捺不住，提高嗓门亮出反潜布局，野心更甚从前。</span></span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="386" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.6967509025270758" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTgGRXM5yrzR372CwxRJSCVFaXmDf2Iwtd2fiaib9NsIQSyfcf3b9yhbyf0YzYpgLbjcKenNYktOXXg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">前言：关于中国军事的相关动态，最关注的除了美国，恐怕就是日本了。前不久，关于解放军核潜艇，外网上又掀起了一次不小的轰动。因为有卫星图片显示</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">解放军最新型攻击核潜艇即将下水，其拥有更好的静音性能，还可以发射巡航导弹</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，而一直打算在东海、台海与解放军较量的日本自卫队，开始“亮剑”了。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">接下来，让我们一起快看一下，为应对解放军核潜艇，日本自卫队会有什么布局，是否研发出了新装备？</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;"><p></p></span></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;">01</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;visibility: visible;"><p style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;visibility: visible;"> <strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">解放军的崛起，“刺激”了日本</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 196px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-indent: 0em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;visibility: visible;">   </span><span style="outline: 0px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);visibility: visible;"></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;">   </span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 196px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-indent: 0em;font-family: Calibri;text-align: justify;visibility: visible;"> </span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">据悉，6月19日到6月25日，巴黎举办了第54届巴黎-布里歇国际航空航天展览会。</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">这是自2021年航展取消以来，两年内的首次航展活动，因此，该活动吸引了全球不少知名航空公司的参加。</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;">比如波音、达索、空客、洛克希德·马丁、巴西航空工业以及中国航空工业等，大概有30万游客参观，可以说，本届巴黎航展是有史以来最大规模的国际航展。</span></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;line-height: 2em;"><br></section><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">据消息称，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">日本川崎重工已经成立了下一代海上反潜巡逻机的开发项目，作为</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">反潜机的后继机</span></span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">。</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">众所周知，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">向来被日本成为是全球最先进的反潜巡逻机，与美军</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-8A</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">“海神”不相上下，尤其强调比运</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">-9</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">反潜机更有优势。</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">值得注意的是，在日本自卫队中，<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>反潜机装备数量并不多，老旧的<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-3C</span>反潜机并未全部退役，如今突然大刀阔斧要往前赶，显然是感受到了解放军的快速崛起，为毫无依据的“威胁”杞人忧天。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="370" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.6678700361010831" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTgGRXM5yrzR372CwxRJSCVCF8sJtMz6Ekw6ibQlwjxwWIn8icLBBzgCFOjzuZdiab5ywfHOEO3icg5qg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">按照日本川崎重工的计划，日本海上自卫队将在<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2040</span>年后装备<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>后继机，因而成立项目组，为研制新一代反潜机做足准备。日本防卫省透露，该计划目前还在讨论阶段，无法公布更多的细节。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">不过日方提到，反潜机未来的发展重点是加强“远程攻击武器”和“先进人工智能”等技术，就目前来看，这项计划真正落成，原型机制造估计得等到<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2030</span>年以后了。<p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">02</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.5pt;"> </span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日本<span style="font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>遥遥领先，连美国都比不上</span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 160px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 宋体;"></span></span></section><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;"><br><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;">值得注意的是，</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong style='font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;'><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日本海上自卫队现役的<span style="font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>反潜机，与美军的<span style="font-family: Calibri;">P-8A</span>是目前全球仅有且投入使用的喷气反潜机，都是世界顶尖级的水平</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;">，无论是飞行距离、挂弹能力、探测能力等等，日本<span style="font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>反潜机的优势都是遥遥领先世界各国的，甚至在部分性能方面，美军<span style="font-family: Calibri;">P-8A</span>都比不上。</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"></span></span></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1694423344887" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1694423344887"></mpcpc><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">资料显示，<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>非常注重提高速度和扩大作战半径，同时也在力求强化机上的任务装备，可以有效执行反潜、反舰、指管通情等机能。同时还配备了<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">HPS-106</span>主动相控阵雷达，机腹位置设置了<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">30</span>个声呐浮标投放口，内置弹舱可以容纳制导鱼雷、反潜炸弹等武器，与<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-3C</span>相同的是，都兼具反潜和反水面作战功能。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="387" data-backw="516" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTgGRXM5yrzR372CwxRJSCVCTLZibmRoxWbkd74kXwtRjRKzenkNsia5XibGyJCNgffzibX8I30ATNVTQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="516" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">目前，美军</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-8A</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">还没有推出后继机的开发计划，德国和法国联合开发的</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">MAWS</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">反潜机还只存在于理论层面，即使开工研制，技术水平也不如</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-8A</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，也就是说，</span></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">日本</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">已经坐在反潜机世界第一的地位，下一代反潜机也根本没有竞争者</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，由此可见，日本的野心，是妄图在未来几十年，牢牢掌握世界反潜机的霸主地位。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">03</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="margin-left: 0pt;outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"> 反<strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">潜优势，何以让日本如此痴迷？</span></strong></span></strong></span><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 16px;"></strong></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">JF-22超高速风洞的应用<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">美国觊觎三峡大坝已久</span></span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">中国“杀手”卫星有多强，美航母无处遁形</span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"> </span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;"></span></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 0em;"><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">有人好奇，日本为什么如此热衷在反潜领域的绝对地位呢？其实，这不光是因为解放军核潜艇的快速发展，美国的影响才是最大的。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">一直以来，日本充当的就是美国“小弟”的角色，海上自卫队这些年的发展也紧跟美国步伐，比较偏重反潜和防空能力，其目的很简单，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">就是为了给美航母编队提供便利，协同作战过程中可执行护航、巡逻、搜索等一系列任务，减轻美军舰艇的作战负担。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">几十年来，日本可以说在美国的庇护下，发展出了一支实力强大、技术先进的反潜巡逻机部队，在西太平洋地区，有效掌握着反潜战优势。近几年来，亚洲地区国家，在中国的影响下着重发展自身国防能力，日本提早布局，以保持未来亚洲局势的反潜优势。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="367" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.6624548736462094" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTgGRXM5yrzR372CwxRJSCVbk9FGd9OeUh18dia3XArlGOLR1SngAIxGtOxDKBMHmLtXOSyDGe4Kibw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">而在这一领域，反潜巡逻机是非常重要的一款装备，其通用能力非常强，不仅可以用来对抗潜艇，还具备对海、对地攻击能力，执行侦查任务也是一个不错的平台。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">还有一个关键的因素，日本作为战败国，是不允许拥有进攻性武器的，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">海上自卫队的诞生也是打着“防御威胁”的旗号的，如此一来更加没有合理的理由发展对地攻击力量，就如今这般景象，已经是美国底线了。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">而且美国还不允许日本购买其他国家的舰对舰导弹，所以日本海自的反舰能力也强不到哪去，在这个背景下，只能专心搞防空和反潜了，但鉴于历史经验，日本是不可能安分守己仅停留在“防御”层面的。<p></p></span></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">04</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="margin-left: 0pt;outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"> <strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发展反潜机是假，轰炸机才是真？</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 10.5pt;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;"></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">中国海军的快速发展</span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 0em;"><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">上述提到，由于战败国《和平宪法》的限制，日本是无法拥有战略轰炸机和核潜艇的，改装的准航母也只能搭载<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">F-35B</span>，打击距离非常有限，现有的<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>反潜机，拥有<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">4000</span>公里的打击距离，是日本打击距离最远的武器。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="358" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.6462093862815884" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTgGRXM5yrzR372CwxRJSCV3iagy8ROWazQmkRibNMFKSmm7TjNmbR3BWUZfYqU7AZTztGGe9ulwybg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">在这个基础上，日本未来新一代反潜机的打击距离怎么也得</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">5000</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">公里开外，但如此一来，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">日本所谓的反潜机，已经实质意义上变成了“洲际战略武器”，新型反潜机计划也将成为远程轰炸机开发计划</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，新一代反潜机作战效能对标的可能就是美军的</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">B-1B</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">B-51</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">轰炸机，或许，这才是日本此次计划背后的真正目的。</span></span></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1694423589244" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1694423589244"></mpcpc><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"></span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">这是值得我们警惕的，近些年来，日本不时试探导弹威胁，各项演习只是表现之一，一来是为了渲染地区紧张局势，为扩充军备找寻借口，构建新的美日防御体系，加强东亚地区美日军事一体化；<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">二来，日本政府早已受够宪法束缚，<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2017</span>年，日本从美国引进两套陆基“宙斯盾”反导系统，当时就有人表示，虽然“宙斯盾”名义上是反导系统，但如果装备巡航导弹的话，就可以成为攻击敌方目标的有力武器，可见，日方一直在试图扭转宪法给国内造成的“颓势”。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="365" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.6588447653429603" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gTgGRXM5yrzR372CwxRJSCVAJGIKr0vNaXdu1064mic5lHtKibooibnkJKWJdnbLUOaDSoAa9Uw74U2Q/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="123380" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">05</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="margin-left: 0pt;outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"> <strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">解放军运<span style="font-family: Calibri;">-9</span>，任重而道远</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 10.5pt;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;"></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">中国海军的快速发展</span></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin-left: -20px;outline: 0px;width: 214px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 10.5pt;font-family: Calibri;break-before: auto;break-after: auto;word-break: normal;direction: ltr;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;">在这个背景下，为维护亚太地区和平稳定，我国运<span style="font-family: Calibri;">-9</span>反潜机可谓是任重而道远。据悉，</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong style='font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;'><span style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-family: 宋体;">运<span style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-family: Calibri;">-9</span>动力系统仍然采用的是涡轮螺旋桨发动机，这种设计无论是速度、航程还是武器载荷，都与四发喷气式推进的<span style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-family: Calibri;">P-1</span>反潜机存在一定的差距。</span></strong></span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">至于喷气反潜机，我国距离实用化也有一段路程需要走，主要是缺少一个合适的喷气式平台。不过，运<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">-9</span>采用的大量技术都是国产的，整体性能比运<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">-8</span>反潜巡逻机有明显提高。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">另外，国产民用客机也步入了快车道，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">我们可以考虑使用喷气式客机进行改装新一代反潜巡逻机，例如</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">C919</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">就是一个不错的改装平台</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，后续如果核心子系统都能完成国产化，那么下一代反潜机或许可以采用这个思路，我们可以浅浅期待一下。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">整体来看，解放军海上力量更着重均衡发展。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">结语：关于日本下一代海上反潜巡逻机，大家还有什么了解的吗？欢迎在评论区留下您的看法和故事。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.5pt;"><p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;">点亮【在看】，持续关注更多精彩内容</span></p><p><br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1934559687" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
